high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the fridge.
Pick up the left side mango out of two from the down rack of the fridge.
Go right towards the sink.
Put the mango in the sink.
Come back towards the fridge.
Pick up the second mango from the fridge.
Turn right and walk towards the sink.
Put the second mango back side of the first mango into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two mangoes into the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk straight to reach the fridge
Open the fridge and take a mango from it and close the fridge
Turn right and walk towards sink
Put the mango in the sink
Turn back and walk towards the fridge on the right side
Open the fridge and take a mango from it and close the fridge
Turn right and walk towards sink again
Put the mango in the sink along with the first mango
anns.task_desc: Put the mango in the sink

high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the fridge.
Pick up mango from the fridge.
Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the sink.
Place mango on the sink.
Turn around and turn left and then head straight towards the fridge.
Pick up mango from the fridge.
Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the sink.
Place mango on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Collecting mango from different places and arranging them on a sink.
